Template: x10-widget/dbus-isServer
Type: select
Choices: Client, Controller
Default: Controller
Description: Configure as
 Does this machine directly controls the CM19A USB device or does it connect to a remote controller.

Template: x10-widget/dbus-local-address
Type: string
Default: 127.0.0.1
Description: DBUS Listening Interface
 What is the public interface (i.e. eth0's IP) this daemon should listen to for incoming commmands?
 .
 this will open a DBUS daemon listening on that address.

Template: x10-widget/dbus-local-port
Type: string
Default: 14500
Description: DBUS Listening Port
 What is the port this daemon should listen to

Template: x10-widget/dbus-remote-port
Type: string
Default: 14500
Description: DBUS Remote Port
 Enter the port used for the controller

Template: x10-widget/dbus-remote-address
Type: string
Default: 127.0.0.1
Description: DBUS Remote Host
 Enter the IP's host of the X10 Controller